Ama, buksan mo ang pinto!

00:10:43.340 --> 00:10:44.819
Mangyaring pumasok dito,

00:10:44.820 --> 00:10:46.059
Ama.

00:10:46.820 --> 00:10:48.620
Feng Qingfeng

00:10:49.460 --> 00:10:52.540
Hindi na kita kokontrahin.

00:10:53.580 --> 00:10:54.900
Ama!

00:11:04.659 --> 00:11:08.219
Pinasisigla mo ang apoy na ito
ng sarili mong buhay para labanan ako.

00:11:09.259 --> 00:11:13.380
Bilang pitumpu't dalawang pinuno
ng pamilya Feng,

00:11:13.539 --> 00:11:18.459
Isinusumpa ko na poprotektahan ito ng aking buhay!

00:11:40.100 --> 00:11:41.739
Ama!

00:11:42.580 --> 00:11:44.579
Feng Qingfeng!

00:12:01.259 --> 00:12:02.459
Ginoong Feng.

00:12:27.499 --> 00:12:29.418
(Hinayaan ko ang aking pagmamataas na mas mahusay sa akin.)

00:12:29.419 --> 00:12:30.498
Ginoong Feng.

00:12:30.499 --> 00:12:31.939
(Wala si Shang)

00:12:32.340 --> 00:12:33.939
(at ang mga Dragons,)

00:12:34.619 --> 00:12:37.459
(Ako pa rin ang Feng Zhilou
na wala.)

00:12:37.659 --> 00:12:39.140
(Ito ako,)

00:12:39.259 --> 00:12:41.540
(at ang pamilyang Feng ay pareho.)

00:12:58.940 --> 00:13:00.099
Feng Zhilou

00:13:00.700 --> 00:13:02.819
walang tao sa pamilya mo

00:13:03.259 --> 00:13:05.140
aalis ng buhay ngayon!

00:13:07.100 --> 00:13:08.780
Nakaligtas ka?

00:13:11.220 --> 00:13:13.260
Hindi ba obvious?

00:13:14.419 --> 00:13:16.380
Sa wakas ay namumuo na ang takot.

00:13:16.860 --> 00:13:18.819
Hindi ba't medyo huli na iyon?

00:13:19.340 --> 00:13:20.979
Nang walang proteksyon ng mga Dragon,

00:13:21.259 --> 00:13:23.459
ikaw at ang pamilya Feng

00:13:23.460 --> 00:13:25.300
ay walang iba kundi alikabok sa akin!

00:13:25.580 --> 00:13:27.260
Ganap na hindi gaanong mahalaga!

00:13:47.580 --> 00:13:48.699
Ama.

00:13:56.580 --> 00:13:58.540
papatayin kita!

00:14:42.379 --> 00:14:43.739
hindi kita hahayaan...

00:14:45.460 --> 00:14:47.620
saktan ang sinuman sa pamilya Feng...

00:14:49.019 --> 00:14:50.339
kailanman muli.

00:14:51.100 --> 00:14:52.540
Naniniwala ka ba talaga

00:14:53.019 --> 00:14:54.620
ang isang talunan na tulad mo ay karapat-dapat na pigilan ako?

00:15:11.060 --> 00:15:13.140
Ang aking ama ay hindi kailanman yumukod sa iyo,

00:15:14.300 --> 00:15:15.939
at ako, si Feng Zhilou,

00:15:16.860 --> 00:15:19.020
hindi rin.

00:15:28.659 --> 00:15:30.180
Siyam na espirituwal na ugat?

00:15:31.100 --> 00:15:32.579
Iyan ay siyam na espirituwal na ugat.

00:15:32.659 --> 00:15:35.819
Si Zhilou ang tunay na martial prodigy!

00:15:36.100 --> 00:15:37.219
Imposible.

